    &lt;/figure&gt;

  &lt;p id="ONErOb"&gt;Amazon’s second &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/24255302/amazon-prime-day-deals-tips-news-guide-2024-october"&gt;Prime Day&lt;/a&gt; of the year is bringing &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/good-deals/24262468/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sales-tech-gadgets-october-2024"&gt;serious savings across the board&lt;/a&gt;, but some deals truly stand out. Take the &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/23365910/apple-airpods-pro-second-generation-review"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AirPods Pro 2&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, for example — the pair that comes with a USB-C charging case has &lt;a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0D1XD1ZV3?tag=theverge02-20" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;plummeted all the way to $168.99&lt;/a&gt; (about $81 off) for Prime members, matching the all-time low. &lt;/p&gt;
