      &lt;img alt="TikTok name logo on a black background with repeating pink and aqua colored logos" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/bfWofgQ4jhZOi-HIi_HnjGYX8qk=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73639684/STK051_VRG_Illo_N_Barclay_9_tiktok.0.jpg" /&gt;
