    &lt;/figure&gt;

  &lt;p id="6SIrOL"&gt;Every month or so, we like to ask our staff &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/22344288/favorite-gadgets-tech-lgear-aptops-headphones-kitchen-recommendations"&gt;about their favorite stuff&lt;/a&gt; — whether it’s board games, smart tech, or kitchen gadgets. And the results are usually very different, very interesting, and a lot of fun.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="c-float-left c-float-hang"&gt;&lt;aside id="CP4RWK"&gt;&lt;div data-anthem-component="readmore" data-anthem-component-data='{"stories":[{"title":"The best deals from Amazon’s October Prime Day sale","url":"https://www.theverge.com/good-deals/24262468/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sales-tech-gadgets-october-2024"},{"title":"How to find the best deals during Amazon’s fall Prime Day sale","url":"https://www.theverge.com/21502865/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-how-to-find"},{"title":"The best October Prime Day deals you can get for under $100","url":"https://www.theverge.com/24264356/amazon-prime-day-best-cheap-tech-deals-under-100-october-2024"}]}'&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/aside&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p id="Cl5ECB"&gt;Since Amazon is pushing a lot of deals as part of its &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/24255302/amazon-prime-day-deals-tips-news-guide-2024-october"&gt;October Prime Day event&lt;/a&gt;, we looked through some of our recent “favorites” articles and found deals on a lot of the devices we like. So, we thought we’d list a few in case you have read about them in the past and thought, well, that sort of sounds good, but it’s a bit pricey. (Or — that’s pretty cheap, but maybe I’ll wait until the price goes down even more...)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id="37Gn4T"&gt;What follows are some of our staff’s most-liked stuff for the home and office.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="60YQAl"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For the office&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2 id="TRugrp"&gt;Neon sign&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p id="687bZx"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Kylie Robison,...&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;
    &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/24265074/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sale-tech-staff-picks-favorites-october-2024"&gt;Continue reading&amp;hellip;&lt;/a&gt;
